20 void FlashTank::calculateProperties()
21 {
22  auto sp = SteamProperties(inletWaterPressure, quantityType, quantityValue).calculate();
23  inletWaterProperties = {inletWaterMassFlow, inletWaterMassFlow * sp.specificEnthalpy, sp};
24 
25  auto saturatedProperties = SaturatedProperties(tankPressure, SaturatedTemperature(tankPressure).calculate()).calculate();
26  double liquidMassFlow;
27  if (inletWaterProperties.specificEnthalpy > saturatedProperties.gasSpecificEnthalpy)
28  {
29  liquidMassFlow = 0;
30  // TODO question density is 0 below bc saturated properties doesn't return density, same with both sp objects here
31  sp = {
32  saturatedProperties.temperature, saturatedProperties.pressure, 0,
33  saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificVolume, 0,
34  saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEnthalpy, saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEntropy};
35  outletLiquidSaturatedProperties = {
36  liquidMassFlow,
37  liquidMassFlow * saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEnthalpy,
38  sp};
39  }
40  else if (inletWaterProperties.specificEnthalpy < saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEnthalpy)
41  {
42  liquidMassFlow = inletWaterMassFlow;
43  outletLiquidSaturatedProperties = inletWaterProperties;
44  }
45  else
46  {
47  liquidMassFlow = inletWaterMassFlow * (inletWaterProperties.specificEnthalpy - saturatedProperties.gasSpecificEnthalpy) / (saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEnthalpy - saturatedProperties.gasSpecificEnthalpy);
48  // TODO question density is 0 below bc saturated properties doesn't return density, same with both sp objects here
49  sp = {
50  saturatedProperties.temperature, saturatedProperties.pressure, 0,
51  saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificVolume, 0,
52  saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEnthalpy, saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEntropy};
53 
54  outletLiquidSaturatedProperties = {
55  liquidMassFlow,
56  liquidMassFlow * saturatedProperties.liquidSpecificEnthalpy,
57  sp};
58  }
59 
60  sp = {
61  saturatedProperties.temperature, saturatedProperties.pressure, 1,
62  saturatedProperties.gasSpecificVolume, 0,
63  saturatedProperties.gasSpecificEnthalpy, saturatedProperties.gasSpecificEntropy};
64 
65  double const gasMassFlow = inletWaterMassFlow - outletLiquidSaturatedProperties.massFlow;
66  outletGasSaturatedProperties = {gasMassFlow, gasMassFlow * sp.specificEnthalpy, sp};
67 }
